<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm17219040">
<term>absolute advantage</term><meaning id="fs-idp39928784">when one country can use fewer resources to produce a good compared to another country; when a country is more productive compared to another country</meaning>
</definition>

<definition id="fs-idp148885792">
<term>gain from trade</term><meaning id="fs-idp121659664">a country that can consume more than it can produce as a result of specialization and trade</meaning>
</definition>
